Description: Minimum position of modulo range.The minimum position value of the modulo rangemust be less than the maximum position value ofthe modulo range.The value must not exceed the maximum possiblevalue of position scaling _ScalePOSmax.Setting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active immediately.Available with firmware version ≥V01.01.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 3006:39hModbus 1650Profibus 1650CIP 106.1.57ModbusTCP 1650EtherCAT 3006:39hPROFINET 1650

Description: Maximum position of modulo range.The maximum position value of the modulo rangemust be greater than the minimum position valueof the modulo range.The value must not exceed the maximum possiblevalue of position scaling _ScalePOSmax.Setting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active immediately.Available with firmware version ≥V01.01.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 3006:3AhModbus 1652Profibus 1652CIP 106.1.58ModbusTCP 1652EtherCAT 3006:3AhPROFINET 1652
